ormat-check` all clean.\n\n## Technical Approach\n\n### Delete old test file\n\n```bash\ngit rm tests/test_builtins.py\n```\n\n### Audit `__init__.py`\n\nEnsure it only contains:\n- Imports from `_registry` (`BUILTINS`, `BuiltInFunc`, `builtin`)\n- Submodule imports to trigger registration\n- `__all__` re-exports\n- No function bodies\n\n### Audit `_shared.py`\n\nVerify each helper in `_shared.py` is imported by 2+ submodules. If any helper is used by only one, move it into that submodule.\n\n### Import site verification\n\n```bash\ngrep -rn \"from darkfactory.builtins import\" src/ tests/ workflows/\ngrep -rn \"from darkfactory import builtins\" src/ tests/ workflows/\n```\n\nConfirm all import sites resolve without error.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] AC-1: `tests/test_builtins.py` is deleted.\n- [ ] AC-2: `builtins/__init__.py` contains only imports and re-exports — no builtin implementations.\n- [ ] AC-3: Every helper in `_shared.py` is used by 2+ builtins.\n- [ ] AC-4: All `from darkfactory.builtins import X` sites in the codebase resolve.\n- [ ] AC-5: All tests pass. `just test`, `just lint`, `just typecheck`, `just format-check` all clean.\n- [ ] AC-6: No dead code remains from the old monolith.\n","numLines":85,"startLine":1,"totalLines":85}}}
